                       |                 |
           ^ |         |        |        |        |
           | `------.  |        |        |        |
           |        |  |        |        |        |
           v        v  |        |        |        |
                                |                 |
        [scan]   [arg-source]   `-->  [logic]     `-->  [cmd-sink]

                                       ^ ^ ^                ^
                                       | | |                |
                     ,-----------------' | |                |
                     |           ,-------' `---.            |
                     |           |             |            |
                     v           v             v            v

                  [cache] [transform.sed] [transform]   [buildcmd]

